## Proposed Changes

### 1. Email Service

#### [NEW] `src/lib/email.ts`
Create a Nodemailer-based email utility:
- Configure SMTP transporter from environment variables
- `sendNotificationEmail(data)` — sends a styled HTML email with full form details to the official CYROTICS email
- `sendAutoReplyEmail(data)` — sends a professional confirmation email to the user acknowledging their inquiry
- Graceful error handling — email failures should be logged but **not** block form submission (the DB save is the critical path)

---

### 2. Server Action Update

#### [MODIFY] [actions.ts](file:///c:/Users/EDAG-LAB/Downloads/project/src/app/actions.ts)
After the successful database insert (`stmt.run(dbData)`):
- Call `sendNotificationEmail()` with the validated form data
- Call `sendAutoReplyEmail()` with the user's email and name
- Both calls will be fire-and-forget (non-blocking) so form submission remains fast

---

### 3. Spam Protection — Rate Limiting

#### [NEW] `src/lib/rate-limit.ts`
In-memory rate limiter (no external dependencies):
- Track submissions by IP address using a `Map<string, { count, resetTime }>`
- Limit: **3 submissions per 15 minutes** per IP
- Auto-cleanup of expired entries
- Returns `{ success: boolean, remaining: number }`

#### [MODIFY] [actions.ts](file:///c:/Users/EDAG-LAB/Downloads/project/src/app/actions.ts)
- Import the rate limiter
- Check rate limit before processing the form
- Return a clear error message if rate limit is exceeded

